data.title: Public Skating at Brooks School
data.meta_description: Public Skating at Brooks School is held Sunday nights in the winter, and it raises money for our Summer Shows on the Common.
data.text:
Thank you for joining us at Sunday Night Skating at Brooks School for Winter 2024! We had an awesome 8 weeks of skating for NA Residents from January 14th - March 3rd. Each winter we run this program for 8 weeks at Brooks School on Sundays from 6:30-8:30.

Thank you to our Skating staff, Brooks School, and everyone who attended the program this winter. All money raised from Sunday Night Skating at Brooks School goes towards our Summer Children's Shows and Concerts on the Common!
